Medium-sized leafhoppers (
Fig. 6A–B
). Head in dorsal view (
Fig. 1A
) moderately produced anteriorly, median length of crown slightly less than interocular width; in lateral view (
Fig. 1C
), with crown-face transition with anterior margin foliaceous and bicarinate. Forewing (
Fig. 1D
